1
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:21,000
Enter Kratos Core: An autonomous, AI-driven asset management engine built natively for the Mantle Network.

2
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:25,000
We are not just building another yield aggregator.

3
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:32,500
We are building a fully autonomous hedge fund that operates with zero human emotion and strict institutional guardrails.

4
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:36,500
At the heart of Kratos is our dual-LLM architecture.

5
00:00:36,500 --> 00:00:42,000
A custom Python ingestion daemon continuously pulls live macroeconomic data.

6
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:50,000
Gemini 3.5 Flash serves as our Chief Investment Officer, synthesizing global liquidity and risk sentiment into a macro thesis.

7
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:55,000
This thesis is immediately handed off to Mistral 7B, our quantitative structurer,

8
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:02,000
which translates the sentiment into precise mathematical allocations across three premium Mantle assets:

9
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:11,000
Ondo U.S. Dollar Yield for baseline stability, staked ether for liquid staking yield, and fBTC for macro Bitcoin exposure.

10
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:15,000
But AI hallucinates. How do we trust it with capital?

11
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:18,500
We don't. Before any transaction is signed,

12
00:01:18,500 --> 00:01:25,500
our execution engine forces the AI's proposed allocations through hard-coded, zero-trust institutional guardrails.

13
00:01:25,500 --> 00:01:33,000
It actively verifies OFAC compliance, enforces strict maximum drawdowns, and limits volatility caps.

14
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:39,000
Only if every single security constraint passes does the agent cryptographically sign the payload

15
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:45,000
and broadcast it directly to our custom Solidity Vault on the Mantle testnet.

16
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:51,000
No human intervention. Zero mock data. Everything is verifiable on-chain.

17
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:58,500
To bridge the gap between AI autonomy and human oversight, we built a premium React telemetry dashboard.

18
00:01:58,500 --> 00:02:03,500
Investors can monitor Total Value Locked, track live allocations,

19
00:02:03,500 --> 00:02:11,000
and watch the AI Awakening Stream, a raw, real-time terminal feed of the agent's internal reasoning,

20
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:16,000
compliance checks, and live Mantle transaction hashes.

21
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:23,180
Kratos Core outpaces manual risk management, bringing transparency to DeFi.

